<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="26Sep1932"><font color="red">26 September 1932</font> <i>Beach Letters</i> (to Sylvia Beach): Vogt &hellip; operation too difficult &hellip; I have to go back to Zurich every 3 months for the next year and a quarter &hellip; This summer like the beard of Polonius is far too long. I have been trying to work for the new Transition </div>
